    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，起点是HIPAA_Vault。我注意到您提到EMR_Sync，但流程里好像有两个EMR_Sync节点？一个是发送端，另一个是接收HTTP请求的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，确实有两个EMR_Sync实例。第一个是B节点，负责发起HTTP请求；第二个是C节点，接收请求并做后续处理。这样设计是为了解耦内外网的数据交换。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经画好了A到B的\"Envia datos\"箭头，以及B到C的\"Petició HTTP\"箭头。接下来C节点应该连到哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "C节点要把数据传给LabAnalyzer，也就是D节点，关系是\"Valida datos\"。LabAnalyzer会验证实验数据的完整性。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "C到D的验证箭头已添加。LabAnalyzer验证完之后需要回查原始数据吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，D节点要向E节点查询，E节点是另一个HIPAA_Vault实例，专门存实验相关的加密数据。箭头标注\"Consulta datos\"，然后E要返回数据给D。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：D到E是查询请求，E到D是响应数据，标注\"Responde datos\"。这两个箭头方向相反，形成一次往返通信，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。LabAnalyzer拿到数据后，要把处理结果沿原路返回。D返回给C是\"Devuelve datos\"，然后C到B是\"Respuesta HTTP\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "D到C、C到B的返回箭头都已画好。最后B节点应该回到HIPAA_Vault吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，最后一个节点F，也是HIPAA_Vault，但和A、E是不同实例。B把\"Datos procesados\"发给F，完成整个闭环。这样数据从保险库出发，经过EMR同步、LabAnalyzer验证，最终处理结果存回另一个保险库分区。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "流程图已完成。我检查一下：三个HIPAA_Vault实例A、E、F分别位于流程的起点、中间查询点和终点，两个EMR_Sync实例B、C负责内外网桥接，LabAnalyzer D做核心验证。整个数据流有去有回，最终处理结果归档到F节点。结构符合HIPAA合规要求吗？",
